April 7, 2016

- able to download mautic through https://github.com/mautic/mautic
- extract the mautic package in the desired location
- can accept a string that can be used as the branding name, and 
  named the mautic folder to the entered branding name
- able to unpack the mautic zip file to desired location but have a 
  default location if not specified
- able to call composer update once the unpacking is done
